From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: MC20018 <winme2001@outlook.com>
Date: Tue, 23 Jun 2026 20:12:18 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Fand: optimize packet fanout and AI hot paths

Reuse encoded packet buffers across repeated sends, add packet-level cache invalidation hooks, and reduce per-tick entity sensor allocations for high-player-count simulations.

